53
00:03:26.900 --> 00:03:30.760
antigens presented on MHC, and we'll hear about

54
00:03:30.900 --> 00:03:32.700
TCR approaches today.

55
00:03:34.180 --> 00:03:37.780
And beyond these genetically engineered approaches, other approaches, as mentioned,

56
00:03:37.820 --> 00:03:41.640
involve expansion of naturally tumor-reactive cells or

