101
00:06:32.788 --> 00:06:36.688
Thirdly, antigen heterogeneity makes it difficult for CAR T,

102
00:06:36.948 --> 00:06:40.428
which targeting a single target to produce the

103
00:06:40.768 --> 00:06:42.308
