539
00:32:35.436 --> 00:32:38.496
exhaust T cells and to fight the tumor and kill the tumor.

540
00:32:39.796 --> 00:32:43.776
So to summarize, the first, the TIL therapy

541
00:32:44.096 --> 00:32:47.446
is active, is worked in acral

542
00:32:47.456 --> 00:32:50.776
melanoma. We have clinical proof.

543
00:32:51.356 --> 00:32:54.976
Second, the production quality is more

544
00:32:55.076 --> 00:32:58.776
important than the quantity because the efficacy is

545
00:32:58.796 --> 00:33:02.566
