546
00:33:02.616 --> 00:33:05.836
exhaust T cells, not the total T cell numbers.

547
00:33:06.436 --> 00:33:06.686
And

548
00:33:08.316 --> 00:33:12.236
the third, the durable immunity comes from the

549
00:33:12.716 --> 00:33:16.616
progenitor exhaust T cells, because

550
00:33:16.696 --> 00:33:20.416
it's seeded by the infused TIL cells in clones.

551
00:33:21.016 --> 00:33:24.676
And the last, we have

552
00:33:24.756 --> 00:33:28.746
actionable biomarkers to predict and monitor

553
00:33:28.816 --> 00:33:31.656
the clinical response in the TIL therapy.

554
00:33:33.196 --> 00:33:37.056
So what's next? Right now, we also set up a Phase II

555
00:33:37.196 --> 00:33:40.876
clinical trial to evaluate the acral melanoma

556
00:33:41.456 --> 00:33:44.176
compared with select chemotherapies.

557
00:33:45.496 --> 00:33:49.416
And also in the future, we already use a new

558
00:33:49.436 --> 00:33:53.296
tool called T-editor, do the CRISPR

559
00:33:53.416 --> 00:33:55.256
mid technology for the TIL

560
00:33:56.616 --> 00:33:59.896
gene editor. And, also we have finished this.

561
00:34:00.436 --> 00:34:04.136
Our preliminary data also shows that this

562
00:34:04.476 --> 00:34:07.876
supercharged TIL product overcomes the

563
00:34:07.976 --> 00:34:11.857
immuno response of TGF-beta signaling in tumor

564
00:34:11.917 --> 00:34:12.536
microenvironment.

565
00:34:13.476 --> 00:34:17.076
The data shows that the supercharged TIL

566
00:34:17.156 --> 00:34:20.736
product can produce much more

567
00:34:20.857 --> 00:34:22.417
interferon gamma and

568
00:34:24.496 --> 00:34:27.736
increase the cytolytic activity.

569
00:34:28.536 --> 00:34:31.437
In animal model, we also can see the

570
00:34:32.156 --> 00:34:36.016
LM030 can increase

571
00:34:36.236 --> 00:34:37.946
the tumor growth inhibition.

572
00:34:39.676 --> 00:34:42.957
So in the future, maybe we'll have three methods to

573
00:34:43.036 --> 00:34:46.476
optimize our TIL therapy. First, we can

574
00:34:47.696 --> 00:34:49.446
optimize the manufacturers,

575
00:34:50.377 --> 00:34:53.976
the TIL therapy products, because we can use small

576
00:34:54.016 --> 00:34:57.576
molecular and cytokines and such things

577
00:34:57.615 --> 00:35:01.136
to make a more optimized products.

578
00:35:01.496 --> 00:35:03.215
Also, we need to find more

579
00:35:04.796 --> 00:35:08.436
good or easily to find biomarkers to predict

580
00:35:08.596 --> 00:35:12.096
or monitor the response. And also we need to

581
00:35:12.376 --> 00:35:15.476
validate these biomarker in the perspective

582
00:35:16.016 --> 00:35:19.916
studies in the future. Also, we can produce more

583
00:35:19.936 --> 00:35:23.436
next generation TIL product to overcome the

584
00:35:23.876 --> 00:35:25.196
immuno resistance in

585
00:35:26.236 --> 00:35:27.636
other solid tumors.

586
00:35:28.716 --> 00:35:31.786
So this is group work and

587
00:35:32.776 --> 00:35:36.636
thanks very much to the Professor Xin Chen and Professor

